casebody.head_matter:
Lakshmi ARUNACHALAM, Petitioner,
v.
LYFT, INC.
No. 19-8029.
Supreme Court of the United States.
May 18, 2020
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8. The Chief Justice took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion and this petition.
